quran[9{c,v,t}:
6,60,"wohi hai jo raat ko tumhari roohein qabz karta hai aur din ko jo kuch tum karte ho usay jaanta hai, phir dosray roz woh tumhe isi kaarobar ke aalam mein wapas bhaij deta hai taakay zindagi ki muqarrar muddat poori ho aakhir-kaar isi ki taraf tumhari wapsi hai, phir o hay tumhe bta day ga ke tum kya karte rahay ho"
6,61,"apne bundon par woh poori qudrat rakhta hai aur tum par nigrani karne walay muqarrar kar ke bhejta hai, yahan taq ke jab tum mein se kisi ki mout ka waqt aa jata hai to is ke beje hue farishtay is ki jaan nikaal letay hain aur apna farz injaam dainay mein zara kotahi nahi karte"
6,62,"phir sab ke sab Allah , apne haqeeqi aaqa ki taraf wapas laaye jatay hain khabardaar ho jao, faisla ke saaray ikhtiyarat isi ko haasil hain aur woh hisaab lainay mein bohat taiz hai"
6,63,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! a noon se pucho, sehraa aur samandar ki tarikeon mein kon tumhe khatraat se bachata hai? ko noon hai jis se tum ( museebat ke waqt ) gur gara, girgira kar aur chupkay chupkay duayen mangte ho? kis se kehte ho ke agar is bulaa se to ne hum ko bacha liya to hum zaroor shukar guzaar hon ge ?"
6,64,"kaho, Allah tumhe uss se aur har takleef se nijaat deta hai phir tum dosaron ko uss ka shareektehra-tay ho"
6,65,"kaho, woh iss par Qadir hai ke tum par koi azaab oopar se nazil kar day, ya tumahray qadmon ke neechay se barpaa kar day, ya tumhe garohoon mein taqseem kar ke aik giroh ko dosray giroh ki taaqat ka maza chukhwaday dekho, hum kis terhan baar baar mukhtalif tareeqon se apni nishanain un ke samnay paish kar rahay hain shayad ke yeh haqeeqat ko samajh len"
6,66,tumhari qoum uss ka inkaar kar rahi hai halaank woh haqeeqat hai inn se keh do ke mein tum par hawala daar nahi banaya gaya hon
6,67,"har khabar ke zahuur mein anay ka aik waqt muqarrar hai, anqareeb tum ko khud injaam maloom ho jaye ga"
6,68,aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! jab tum dekho ke log hamari ayaat par nuqta chainian kar rahay hain to un ke paas se hatt jao yahan taq ke woh is guftagu ko chore kar doosri baton mein lag jayen aur agar kabhi shetan tumhe behlaway mein daal day to jis waqt tumhe is ghalti ka ehsas ho jaye is ke baad phir aisay zalim logon ke paas nah betho
